    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The function returns a numeric value, a decimal or float, representing the percentage of gas billed. The return type is structured to provide a precise percentage value, which is essential for accurate reporting and analysis."
        }
